Package com.ibm.db2.r2dbc

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DB2Blob
    DB2Blob represents a binary large object.
    DB2Clob
    DB2Clob represents a character large object.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DB2ColumnMetadata
    Represents metadata of a column in a DB2 table.
    DB2Connection
    DB2Connection represents the connection to the DB2 database server.
    DB2ConnectionConfiguration
    Stores DB2 Connection Configuration details.
    DB2ConnectionConfiguration.Builder
    A builder for DB2ConnectionConfiguration.
    DB2ConnectionFactory
    A factory object that can create DB2Connection objects.
    DB2ConnectionFactoryMetadata
    Represents metadata of a DB2ConnectionFactory.
    DB2ConnectionPool
    A connection pool for DB2Connections.
    DB2PreparedStatement
    Represents a SQL statement to be executed on the database server.
    DB2Result
    Represents a result information from the DB2 server for a request, both for an update and a query request.
    DB2Row
    Represents a row in the result-set.
    DB2RowMetadata
    Represents metadata of a table row.
    Version
    Represents product name, its version and build date.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    DB2Exception.Type
    Type of error.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    DB2Exception
    Represents an error message from the database server.
